org.glassfish.jersey.client.rx.jsr166e

Interface RxCompletableFutureInvoker

  • All Superinterfaces:
    RxInvoker<CompletableFuture>

    public interface RxCompletableFutureInvoker
extends RxInvoker<CompletableFuture>
    Reactive invoker providing support for CompletableFuture from JSR-166e (pre-Java 8).
    Since:
    2.13
    Author:
    Michal Gajdos
